- cs.NA (Numerical Analysis): The paper discusses the application of numerical methods for solving stochastic differential equations, which falls under the scope of numerical analysis. 
- cs.MS (Mathematical Software): The paper discusses the implementation of software for stochastic numerical methods, which falls under the scope of mathematical software. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses the application of stochastic numerical methods for systems of differential equations, which falls under the scope of systems and control. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): Although not directly related to machine learning, the paper discusses the use of Python and Julia programming languages, which are commonly used in machine learning. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper discusses the difficulties in implementing stochastic numerical methods and the use of source code generation, which falls under the scope of software engineering.
